Kodi Builds

Best Kodi Builds Working Right Now! (Updated May 2024)

  • Last Updated:
  • May 1, 2024

Once you’ve installed Kodi, an option to enhance Kodi is to add a Build. That is because simply installing Kodi onto your device is not enough. You’ll need Kodi Addons or Builds to utilise its full potential. These Addons and Builds give users free content, including movies, shows, live TV channels, sports, music, radio stations, and news.

Given that the status of Builds is constantly changing, updating and disappearing, in the following guide, we will look at the best Kodi Builds that are working right now.

Kodi and Kodi Builds can be installed on almost any device, e.g. Firestick, Fire Cube, Nvidia Shield, Android box, Chromecast, phones, tablets, PCs and more.

The Amazon Firestick is a popular streaming device that offers excellent value for money and can be jailbroken with minimal effort. It is a perfect choice for anyone looking to cut the cord, regardless of their experience with streaming devices.

What is a Kodi Build?

A Kodi Build is a great way to enhance your Kodi experience in one complete installation. A Build can include addons, skins, settings, and more. This can make it very easy to use Kodi with an updated user interface. A Build can encompass everything from free movies, TV shows, and live channels to music and more in one easy-to-install package. 

Are Kodi Builds Safe to Install?

Kodi Builds generally provide free streaming of movies, TV shows, live TV channels etc., to which they do not own the rights to do so. Consequently, using unofficial Builds to stream copyrighted or unlicensed content is unlawful and could get you into trouble. Therefore, a VPN is recommended for safe and anonymous online streaming online. With this in mind, I recommend using NordVPN.
